Reasoning: 
- cs.ET (Embedded Systems): The paper focuses on energy-constrained embedded platforms, which falls under the scope of embedded systems. 
- cs.AR (Hardware Architecture): The paper proposes a communications-inspired approach to design machine learning systems on energy-constrained platforms, which involves hardware architecture design. 
- cs.EM (Emerging Technologies): The paper discusses the use of machine learning on energy-constrained platforms, which can be considered an emerging technology. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the challenges of deploying machine learning on energy-constrained platforms and proposes a communications-inspired approach to address these challenges, which can be seen as a systems and control problem. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper discusses the use of machine learning on energy-constrained platforms and proposes methods to implement machine learning systems on these platforms.
